.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
\fBvoltage <value>\fR: Set the output voltage (in Volts)\&.
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
\fBcurrent\fR
