.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
\fBon\fR
Turn the output on\&.
.RE
.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
hcs voltage 5 output 1\&.3 status
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp
Set the output voltage to 5Volts, the output current limit to 1\&.3Amps and report the current status\&.
